      s.type = 'text/javascript';
      s.async = true;
      s.src = urls[i];
      var x = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
      x.parentNode.insertBefore(s, x);
    }
  };
  document.addEventListener('StartAsyncLoading',function(event){asyncLoad();});if(window.attachEvent) {
    window.attachEvent('onload', function(){});
  } else {
    window.addEventListener('load', function(){}, false);
  }
})();</script>

\u003cspan\u003eE-Mail\u003c\/span\u003e\n    \u003c\/div\u003e\n  \u003c\/a\u003e\n  {% endunless %}\n\u003c\/script\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\n  function appmateSelectCallback(variant, selector) {\n    var shop = Appmate.wk.globals.shop;\n    var product = Appmate.wk.getProduct(variant.product_id);\n    var itemId = Appmate.wk.$(selector.variantIdField).parents('[data-wk-item]').attr('data-wk-item');\n    var container = Appmate.wk.$('#wk-item-' + itemId);\n\n\n    \n\n    var imageUrl = '';\n\n    if (variant \u0026\u0026 variant.image) {\n      imageUrl = Appmate.wk.filters.img_url(variant, '1000x');\n    } else if (product) {\n      imageUrl = Appmate.wk.filters.img_url(product, '1000x');\n    }\n\n    if (imageUrl) {\n      container.find('.wk-variant-image').attr('src', imageUrl);\n    }\n\n    var formatMoney = Appmate.wk.filters.money;\n\n    if (!product.hidden \u0026\u0026 variant \u0026\u0026 (variant.available || variant.inventory_policy === 'continue')) {\n      container.find('.wk-add-to-cart').removeAttr('disabled').removeClass('disabled').attr('value', 'Add to Cart');\n      if(parseFloat(variant.price) \u003c parseFloat(variant.compare_at_price)){\n        container.find('.wk-price-preview').html(formatMoney(variant.price) + \" \u003cdel\u003e\" + formatMoney(variant.compare_at_price) + \"\u003c\/del\u003e\");\n      } else {\n        container.find('.wk-price-preview').html(formatMoney(variant.price));\n      }\n    } else {\n      var message = variant \u0026\u0026 !product.hidden ? \"Notify Me\" : \"Unavailable\";\n      container.find('.wk-add-to-cart').addClass('disabled').attr('disabled', 'disabled').attr('value', message);\n      container.find('.wk-price-preview').text(message);\n    }\n\n  };\n\n  function appmateOptionSelect(el){\n    if (!Shopify || !Shopify.OptionSelectors) {\n      throw new Error('Missing option_selection.js! Please check templates\/page.wishlist.liquid');\n    }\n\n    var id = el.getAttribute('id');\n    var itemId = Appmate.wk.$(el).parents('[data-wk-item]').attr('data-wk-item');\n    var container = Appmate.wk.$('#wk-item-' + itemId);\n\n    Appmate.wk.getItem(itemId).then(function(product){\n      var selector = new Shopify.OptionSelectors(id, {\n        product: product,\n        onVariantSelected: appmateSelectCallback,\n        enableHistoryState: false\n      });\n\n      if (product.selected_variant_id) {\n        selector.selectVariant(product.selected_variant_id);\n      }\n\n      selector.selectors.forEach(function(selector){\n        if (selector.values.length \u003c 2) {\n          Appmate.wk.$(selector.element).parents(\".selector-wrapper\").css({display: \"none\"});\n        }\n      });\n\n      \/\/ Add label if only one product option and it isn't 'Title'.\n      if (product.options.length == 1 \u0026\u0026 product.options[0] != 'Title') {\n        Appmate.wk.$(container)\n        .find('.selector-wrapper:first-child')\n        .prepend('\u003clabel\u003e' + product.options[0] + '\u003c\/label\u003e');\n      }\n    });\n  }\n\u003c\/script\u003e\n\n\u003cscript src=\"https:\/\/cdn.appmate.io\/legacy-toolkit\/1.4.44\/appmate.js\" async\u003e\u003c\/script\u003e\u003clink href=\"\/\/leset.com\/cdn\/shop\/t\/290\/assets\/appmate-wishlist-king.scss.css?v=96817305393259001671750057609\" rel=\"stylesheet\" \/\u003e");}document.close();</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  function initAppmate(Appmate){
    Appmate.wk.on({
      'click [data-wk-add-product]': eventHandler(function(){
        var productId = this.getAttribute('data-wk-add-product');
        var select = Appmate.wk.$('form select[name="id"]');
        var variantId = select.length ? select.val() : undefined;
        Appmate.wk.addProduct(productId, variantId).then(function(product) {
          var variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant || {};
          sendTracking({
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
            eventAction: 'WK Added Product',
            eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
          }, {
            id: variant.sku || variant.id,
            name: product.title,
            category: product.type,
            brand: product.vendor,
            variant: variant.title,
            price: variant.price
          }, {
            list: "" || undefined
          });
        });
      }),
      'click [data-wk-remove-product]': eventHandler(function(){
        var productId = this.getAttribute('data-wk-remove-product');
        Appmate.wk.removeProduct(productId).then(function(product) {
          var variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant || {};
          sendTracking({
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
            eventAction: 'WK Removed Product',
            eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
          }, {
            id: variant.sku || variant.id,
            name: product.title,
            category: product.type,
            brand: product.vendor,
            variant: variant.title,
            price: variant.price
          }, {
            list: "" || undefined
          });
        });
      }),
      'click [data-wk-remove-item]': eventHandler(function(){
        var itemId = this.getAttribute('data-wk-remove-item');
        fadeOrNot(this, function() {
          Appmate.wk.removeItem(itemId).then(function(product){
            var variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant || {};
            sendTracking({
              hitType: 'event',
              eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
              eventAction: 'WK Removed Product',
              eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
            }, {
              id: variant.sku || variant.id,
              name: product.title,
              category: product.type,
              brand: product.vendor,
              variant: variant.title,
              price: variant.price
            }, {
              list: "" || undefined
            });
          });
        });
      }),
      'click [data-wk-clear-wishlist]': eventHandler(function(){
        var wishlistId = this.getAttribute('data-wk-clear-wishlist');
        Appmate.wk.clear(wishlistId).then(function() {
          sendTracking({
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
            eventAction: 'WK Cleared Wishlist',
            eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
          });
        });
      }),
      'click [data-wk-share]': eventHandler(function(){
        var params = {
          wkShareService: this.getAttribute("data-wk-share-service"),
          wkShare: this.getAttribute("data-wk-share"),
          wkShareImage: this.getAttribute("data-wk-share-image")
        };
        var shareLink = Appmate.wk.getShareLink(params);

        sendTracking({
          hitType: 'event',
          eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
          eventAction: 'WK Shared Wishlist (' + params.wkShareService + ')',
          eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
        });

        switch (params.wkShareService) {
          case 'link':
            Appmate.wk.$('#wk-share-link-text').addClass('wk-visible').find('.wk-text').html(shareLink);
            var copyButton = Appmate.wk.$('#wk-share-link-text .wk-clipboard');
            var copyText = copyButton.html();
            var clipboard = Appmate.wk.clipboard(copyButton[0]);
            clipboard.on('success', function(e) {
              copyButton.html('copied');
              setTimeout(function(){
                copyButton.html(copyText);
              }, 2000);
            });
            break;
          case 'email':
            window.location.href = shareLink;
            break;
          case 'contact':
            var contactUrl = '/pages/contact';
            var message = 'Here is the link to my list:\n' + shareLink;
            window.location.href=contactUrl + '?message=' + encodeURIComponent(message);
            break;
          default:
            window.open(
              shareLink,
              'wishlist_share',
              'height=590, width=770, toolbar=no, menubar=no, scrollbars=no, resizable=no, location=no, directories=no, status=no'
            );
        }
      }),
      'click [data-wk-move-to-cart]': eventHandler(function(){
        // Overrided by 7Q81 (assets/7q81.js)
        return;

        var $elem = Appmate.wk.$(this);
        $form = $elem.parents('form');
        $elem.prop("disabled", true);

        var item = this.getAttribute('data-wk-move-to-cart');
        var formData = $form.serialize();

        fadeOrNot(this, function(){
          Appmate.wk
          .moveToCart(item, formData)
          .then(function(product){
            $elem.prop("disabled", false);

            var variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant || {};
            sendTracking({
              hitType: 'event',
              eventCategory: 'Wishlist',
              eventAction: 'WK Added to Cart',
              eventLabel: 'Wishlist King',
              hitCallback: function() {
                window.scrollTo(0, 0);
                location.reload();
              }
            }, {
              id: variant.sku || variant.id,
              name: product.title,
              category: product.type,
              brand: product.vendor,
              variant: variant.title,
              price: variant.price,
              quantity: 1,
            }, {
              list: "" || undefined
            });
          });
        });
      }),
      'render .wk-option-select': function(elem){
        appmateOptionSelect(elem);
      },
      'login-required': function (intent) {
        var redirect = {
          path: window.location.pathname,
          intent: intent
        };
        window.location = '/account/login?wk-redirect=' + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(redirect));
      },
      'ready': function () {
        fillContactForm();

        var redirect = Appmate.wk.getQueryParam('wk-redirect');
        if (redirect) {
          Appmate.wk.addLoginRedirect(Appmate.wk.$('#customer_login'), JSON.parse(redirect));
        }
        var intent = Appmate.wk.getQueryParam('wk-intent');
        if (intent) {
          intent = JSON.parse(intent);
          switch (intent.action) {
            case 'addProduct':
              Appmate.wk.addProduct(intent.product, intent.variant)
              break;
            default:
              console.warn('Wishlist King: Intent not implemented', intent)
          }
          if (window.history && window.history.pushState) {
            history.pushState(null, null, window.location.pathname);
          }
        }
      }
    });

    Appmate.init({
      shop: {
        domain: 'liana-clothing.myshopify.com'
      },
      session: {
        customer: ''
      },
      globals: {
        settings: {
          app_wk_icon: 'heart',
          app_wk_share_position: 'hidden',
          app_wk_products_per_row: 3,
          money_format: '{{amount_no_decimals_with_comma_separator}}₫',
          root_url: ''
        },
        customer: '',
        customer_accounts_enabled: true,
      },
      wishlist: {
        filter: function(product) {
          return !product.hidden;
        },
        loginRequired: false,
        handle: '/pages/wishlist',
        proxyHandle: "/a/wk",
        share: {
          handle: "/pages/shared-wishlist",
          title: 'My Wishlist',
          description: 'Check out some of my favorite things @ LESET.',
          imageTitle: 'LESET',
          hashTags: 'wishlist',
          twitterUser: false // will be used with via
        }
      }
    });

    function sendTracking(event, product, action) {
      if (typeof fbq === 'function') {
        switch (event.eventAction) {
          case "WK Added Product":
            fbq('track', 'AddToWishlist', {
              value: product.price,
              currency: 'USD'
            });
            break;
        }
      }
      if (typeof ga === 'function') {
        if (product) {
          delete product.price;
          ga('ec:addProduct', product);
        }

        if (action) {
          ga('ec:setAction', 'click', action);
        }

        if (event) {
          ga('send', event);
        }

        if (!ga.loaded) {
          event && event.hitCallback && event.hitCallback()
        }
      } else {
        event && event.hitCallback && event.hitCallback()
      }
    }

    function fillContactForm() {
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', fillContactForm)
      if (document.getElementById('contact_form')) {
        var message = Appmate.wk.getQueryParam('message');
        var bodyElement = document.querySelector("#contact_form textarea[name='contact[body]']");
        if (bodyElement && message) {
          bodyElement.value = message;
        }
      }
    }

    function eventHandler (callback) {
      return function (event) {
        if (typeof callback === 'function') {
          callback.call(this, event)
        }
        if (event) {
          event.preventDefault();
          event.stopPropagation();
        }
      }
    }

    function fadeOrNot(elem, callback){
      if (typeof $ !== "function") {
        callback();
        return;
      }
      var $elem = $(elem);
  	  if ($elem.parents('.wk-fadeout').length) {
        $elem.parents('.wk-fadeout').fadeOut(callback);
      } else {
        callback();
      }
    }
  }
</script>

  {% endif %}
  <a href="{{ wishlist.url }}" class="wk-link wk-{{ wishlist.state }}" title="View Wishlist"><div class="wk-icon">{% include link_icon %}</div><span class="wk-label">Wishlist</span> <span class="wk-count">({{ wishlist.item_count }})</span></a>
</script>

<script id="wishlist-button-wishlist-page" data="product" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">

  {% else %}
    {% assign item_id = product.wishlist_item_id %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if product.in_wishlist and wishlist.read_only == true %}
    {% assign btn_text = '- Wishlist' %}
    {% assign btn_title = 'Remove from Wishlist' %}
    {% assign btn_action = 'wk-remove-product' %}
    {% assign btn_icon = 'wishlist-icon-filled' %}

    {% assign btn_text = '- Wishlist' %}
    {% assign btn_title = 'Remove from Wishlist' %}

    {% assign btn_title = '+ Wishlist' %}
    {% assign btn_action = 'wk-add-product' %}
    {% assign btn_icon = 'wishlist-icon-empty' %}
    {% assign add_class = 'wk-with-hover' %}
  {% endif %}

      {% include btn_icon %}
    </div>

  </button>

<script id="wishlist-collection-loop" data="wishlist" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">
  <div class="grid grid--uniform grid--collection">
    {% assign item_count = 0 %}
    {% for product in wishlist.products %}
      {% assign item_count = item_count | plus: 1 %}
      {% unless limit and item_count > limit %}
        {% assign hide_default_title = false %}
        {% if product.variants.length == 1 and product.variants[0].title contains 'Default' %}
          {% assign hide_default_title = true %}
        {% endif %}

        {% assign items_per_row = settings.app_wk_products_per_row %}
        {% assign wk_item_width = 100 | divided_by: items_per_row %}

        <div data-product-handle={{product.handle}} id="{{product.handle}}" class="grid__item grid-product medium-up--one-third" data-aos="row-of-3">
        {% comment %}<div class="wk-item-column" style="width: {{ wk_item_width }}%">{% endcomment %}
          <div id="wk-item-{{ product.wishlist_item_id }}" class="wk-item {{ wk_item_class }} {% unless wishlist.read_only %}wk-fadeout{% endunless %} grid-product__content" data-wk-item="{{ product.wishlist_item_id }}">
            {% include 'wishlist-collection-product-image' with product %}
            {% include 'wishlist-button-wishlist-page' with product %}
            <div class="grid-product__meta">
              {% include 'wishlist-collection-product-title' with product %}
              {% include 'wishlist-collection-product-price' %}
            </div>
            {% include 'wishlist-collection-product-form' with product %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endunless %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</script>

<script id="wishlist-collection-product-image" data="wishlist" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">
  <div class="wk-image">
    <a href="{{ product | variant_url }}" class="wk-variant-link wk-content" title="View product">
      <img class="grid-product__image lazyloaded"
        src="{{ product | variant_img_url: '1000x' }}"
        alt="{{ product.title }}">
    </a>
  </div>
</script>

<script id="wishlist-collection-product-title" data="wishlist" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">
  {% assign sold_out = true %}
  {% if product.available %}
    {% assign sold_out = false %}
  {% endif %}

  {% assign on_sale = false %}
  {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
    {% assign on_sale = true %}
  {% endif %}

  {% assign product_tags = product.tags | join: ',' %}
  {% assign has_custom_label = false %}
  {% if product_tags contains '_label_' %}
    {% for tag in product.tags %}
      {% if tag contains '_label_' %}
        {% assign tag_starts_with = tag | slice: 0 %}
        {% if tag_starts_with == '_' %}
          {% assign has_custom_label = true %}
          {% assign custom_label = tag | replace: '_label_', '' %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}

  <div class="wk-product-title">
    <a href="{{ product | variant_url }}" class="wk-variant-link" title="View product">
      <div class="grid-product__title grid-product__title--body">
        {{ product.title }}

        {% if has_custom_label %}
          <div class="grid-product__tag grid-product__tag--custom">
            {{ custom_label }}
          </div>
        {% else %}
          {% if sold_out %}
            <div class="grid-product__tag grid-product__tag--sold-out">
              Notify Me
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if on_sale and sold_out == false %}
            <div class="grid-product__tag grid-product__tag--sale">
              Sale
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</script>

<script id="wishlist-collection-product-price" data="wishlist" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">
  {% assign variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant %}
  {% assign on_sale = false %}
  {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
    {% assign on_sale = true %}
  {% endif %}

  <div class="wk-purchase">
    <div class="wk-price wk-price-preview">
      <div class="grid-product__price">
        {% if on_sale %}
          <span class="visually-hidden">Regular Price</span>
          <span class="grid-product__price--original">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Sale Price</span>
        {% endif %}
        {% if product.price_varies %}
          {% assign price = product.price_min | money %}
          From {{ price }}
        {% else %}
          {{ product.price  | money }}
        {% endif %}
        {% if on_sale %}
          {% if settings.product_save_amount %}
            {% if settings.product_save_type == 'dollar' %}
              {% capture saved_amount %}{{ product.compare_at_price | minus: product.price | money }}{% endcapture %}
            {% else %}
              {% capture saved_amount %}{{ product.compare_at_price | minus: product.price | times: 100.0 | divided_by: product.compare_at_price | round }}%{% endcapture %}
            {% endif %}
            <span class="grid-product__price--savings">
              Save {{ saved_amount }}
            </span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endif %}

        {% assign product_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant %}
        {% if product_variant.unit_price_measurement %}
          <div class="product__unit-price">
            {% capture unit_price_base_unit %}
              {% if product_variant.unit_price_measurement %}
                {% if product_variant.unit_price_measurement.reference_value != 1 %}
                  {{ product_variant.unit_price_measurement.reference_value }}
                {% endif %}
                {{ product_variant.unit_price_measurement.reference_unit }}
              {% endif %}
            {% endcapture %}

            {{ product_variant.unit_price | money }}/{{ unit_price_base_unit }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</script>

<script id="wishlist-collection-product-form" data="wishlist" type="text/x-template" app="wishlist-king">
  <form id="wk-add-item-form-{{ product.wishlist_item_id }}" action="/cart/add" method="post" class="wk-add-item-form">

    <!-- Begin product options -->
    <div class="wk-product-options {% if hide_default_title %}wk-no-options{% endif %}">

      <div class="wk-select" {% if hide_default_title %} style="display:none"{% endif %}>
        <select id="wk-option-select-{{ product.wishlist_item_id }}" class="wk-option-select" name="id">

          {% for variant in product.variants %}
          <option value="{{ variant.id }}" {% if variant == product.selected_or_first_available_variant %}selected="selected"{% endif %}>
            {{ variant.title }} - {{ variant.price | money }}
          </option>
          {% endfor %}

        </select>
      </div>

      {% comment %}
        {% if settings.display_quantity_dropdown and product.available %}
        <div class="wk-selector-wrapper">
          <label>Quantity</label>
          <input class="wk-quantity" type="number" name="quantity" value="1" class="wk-item-quantity" />
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endcomment %}

      <div class="wk-purchase-section{% if product.variants.length > 1 %} wk-multiple{% endif %}">
        {% unless product.available %}
        <input type="submit" class="wk-add-to-cart disabled" disabled="disabled" value="Notify Me" />
        {% else %}
          {% assign cart_action = 'wk-move-to-cart' %}
          {% if wishlist.read_only %}
            {% assign cart_action = 'wk-add-to-cart' %}
          {% endif %}
          <input type="submit" class="wk-add-to-cart" data-{{ cart_action }}="{{ product.wishlist_item_id }}" name="add" value="Add to Cart" />
        {% endunless %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End product options -->
  </form>
</script>

<script>
  function appmateSelectCallback(variant, selector) {
    var shop = Appmate.wk.globals.shop;
    var product = Appmate.wk.getProduct(variant.product_id);
    var itemId = Appmate.wk.$(selector.variantIdField).parents('[data-wk-item]').attr('data-wk-item');
    var container = Appmate.wk.$('#wk-item-' + itemId);


    

    var imageUrl = '';

    if (variant && variant.image) {
      imageUrl = Appmate.wk.filters.img_url(variant, '1000x');
    } else if (product) {
      imageUrl = Appmate.wk.filters.img_url(product, '1000x');
    }

    if (imageUrl) {
      container.find('.wk-variant-image').attr('src', imageUrl);
    }

    var formatMoney = Appmate.wk.filters.money;

    if (!product.hidden && variant && (variant.available || variant.inventory_policy === 'continue')) {
      container.find('.wk-add-to-cart').removeAttr('disabled').removeClass('disabled').attr('value', 'Add to Cart');
      if(parseFloat(variant.price) < parseFloat(variant.compare_at_price)){
        container.find('.wk-price-preview').html(formatMoney(variant.price) + " <del>" + formatMoney(variant.compare_at_price) + "</del>");
      } else {
        container.find('.wk-price-preview').html(formatMoney(variant.price));
      }
    } else {
      var message = variant && !product.hidden ? "Notify Me" : "Unavailable";
      container.find('.wk-add-to-cart').addClass('disabled').attr('disabled', 'disabled').attr('value', message);
      container.find('.wk-price-preview').text(message);
    }

  };

  function appmateOptionSelect(el){
    if (!Shopify || !Shopify.OptionSelectors) {
      throw new Error('Missing option_selection.js! Please check templates/page.wishlist.liquid');
    }

    var id = el.getAttribute('id');
    var itemId = Appmate.wk.$(el).parents('[data-wk-item]').attr('data-wk-item');
    var container = Appmate.wk.$('#wk-item-' + itemId);

    Appmate.wk.getItem(itemId).then(function(product){
      var selector = new Shopify.OptionSelectors(id, {
        product: product,
        onVariantSelected: appmateSelectCallback,
        enableHistoryState: false
      });

      if (product.selected_variant_id) {
        selector.selectVariant(product.selected_variant_id);
      }

      selector.selectors.forEach(function(selector){
        if (selector.values.length < 2) {
          Appmate.wk.$(selector.element).parents(".selector-wrapper").css({display: "none"});
        }
      });

      // Add label if only one product option and it isn't 'Title'.
      if (product.options.length == 1 && product.options[0] != 'Title') {
        Appmate.wk.$(container)
        .find('.selector-wrapper:first-child')
        .prepend('<label>' + product.options[0] + '</label>');
      }
    });
  }
</script>

  GIST.f._isEmpty = function(obj){

    for(var prop in obj) {
      if(obj.hasOwnProperty(prop)) {
        return false;
      }
    }

    return JSON.stringify(obj) === JSON.stringify({});

  };

  GIST.bundles   = [];
  GIST.remove    = {};
  GIST.discounts = [];

  if (GIST.remove && !GIST.f._isEmpty(GIST.remove) ) {

    GIST.xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
    GIST.xhr.open('POST', Shopify.routes.root + 'cart/update.js');
    GIST.xhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
    GIST.xhr.onload = function() {
      if (GIST.xhr.status === 200 && window.performance) {
         var navEntries = window.performance.getEntriesByType('navigation');
         if (navEntries.length > 0 && navEntries[0].type === 'back_forward') {
            location.reload();
         } else if (window.performance.navigation && window.performance.navigation.type == window.performance.navigation.TYPE_BACK_FORWARD) {
            location.reload();
         }
       }
    };
    GIST.xhr.send(JSON.stringify({updates:GIST.remove}));

  }

  <!-- BEGIN app snippet: recording_consent --><script type="text/javascript">
    const isConsented = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search).get('consent') === 'true';
    const recordSubmitted = 'false' === 'true';
    const shopID = '30125';

    function setSessionStorageWithExpiration(name, value, minutes) {
        const expirationTime = new Date().getTime() + (minutes * 60 * 1000); // Current time + minutes
        const item = {
            value: value,
            expiration: expirationTime
        };
        sessionStorage.setItem(name, JSON.stringify(item));
    }

    function getSessionStorageWithExpiration(name) {
        const itemStr = sessionStorage.getItem(name);
        if (!itemStr) return null;

        try {
            const item = JSON.parse(itemStr);
            const currentTime = new Date().getTime();
            if (currentTime > item.expiration) {
                sessionStorage.removeItem(name);
                return null;
            }
            return item.value;
        } catch (e) {
            sessionStorage.removeItem(name);
            return null;
        }
    }

    const sessionName = 'smartlookRecorded';
    const sessionValue = getSessionStorageWithExpiration(sessionName);

    if (sessionValue || (!recordSubmitted && isConsented)) {

        setSessionStorageWithExpiration(sessionName, 'true', 10);

        window.smartlook || (function (d) {
            var o = smartlook = function () {
                o.api.push(arguments)
            }, h = d.getElementsByTagName('head')[0];
            var c = d.createElement('script');
            o.api = new Array();
            c.async = true;
            c.type = 'text/javascript';
            c.charset = 'utf-8';
            c.src = 'https://web-sdk.smartlook.com/recorder.js';
            h.appendChild(c);
        })(document);
        smartlook('init', '8b4334d2d0097558bc84984a05b3731d38c0e771', {region: 'eu'});
        smartlook('record', {forms: true, numbers: true});
        smartlook('identify', window.Shopify.shop);
        if (!sessionValue) {
            window.fetch(`https://api.fastbundle.co/v3/submit-smartlook-record/${shopID}/`, {
                method: 'PATCH',
                body: JSON.stringify({}) // empty object as the body
            })
                .then(response => response.json())
                .then(data => console.log(data))
                .catch(console.log);
        }
    }

  <script>
    (() => {
      const searchButton = document.querySelector('.site-nav__link--icon.js-search-header');
      const searchContainer = document.querySelector('.site-header__search-container');

      const positionSearchBar = (evt) => {
        setTimeout(() => {
          if (document.documentElement.clientWidth > 1199) {
            const target = evt.target.closest('.site-nav__icons') || evt.target;
            const clientRect = (target).getBoundingClientRect();

            searchContainer.style.top = target.offsetTop + 'px';
            searchContainer.style.left = (clientRect.left - searchContainer.clientWidth - 30) + 'px';
          } else {
            searchContainer.style.top = document.querySelector('.header-sticky-wrapper').clientHeight + 'px';
            searchContainer.style.left = 0;
          }
        }, 25);
      };

      if (searchButton && searchContainer) {
        searchButton.addEventListener('click', positionSearchBar);
      }

      const handleMegamenuHover = (evt) => {
        document.body.classList.add('megamenu-active');
      };

      const handleMegamenuHoverOut = (evt) => {
        document.body.classList.remove('megamenu-active');
      };

      document.querySelectorAll('.site-nav--is-megamenu.site-nav--has-dropdown').forEach((item) => {
        item.addEventListener('mouseenter', handleMegamenuHover);

        item.addEventListener('mouseleave', handleMegamenuHoverOut);
      });
    })();
  </script>
</div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

<script>
  (() => {
    const positionDrawerMenu = (evt) => {
      const header = document.querySelector('header.site-header');
      const headerLayout = document.querySelector('.site-header-sticky .site-header .header-layout');
      const headerHeight = headerLayout.clientHeight + 1;
      const announcementBar = document.querySelector('.announcement-bar--above-header');
      const announcementBarItem = document.querySelectorAll('.qb-multi-announcement-bar-block');

      let announcementBarHeight = 0;

      if (announcementBar) {
        announcementBarHeight = announcementBar.clientHeight;
      }
      if (announcementBarItem) {
        announcementBarItem.forEach(function(this_click){
          if(this_click.clientHeight != 0){
             announcementBarHeight = this_click.clientHeight;
          }
        });
      }
    };

    const positionDrawerCart = (evt) => {
      const header = document.querySelector('.site-header-sticky .site-header');
      const headerHeight = header.clientHeight;
      const announcementBar = document.querySelector('.announcement-bar--above-header');
      let announcementBarHeight = 0;

      if (announcementBar) {
        announcementBarHeight = announcementBar.clientHeight;
      }

      document.getElementById('CartDrawer').style.top = (header.classList.contains('site-header--stuck') ? headerHeight : (headerHeight + announcementBarHeight)) + 'px';
    };

    window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
        positionDrawerMenu();
    }, true);

    document.querySelectorAll('.mobile-nav__has-sublist')?.forEach(li => {
      li?.addEventListener('click', handleDrawerItemClick);
    });

    document.querySelectorAll('.drawer-controls__button.js-drawer-back').forEach(btn => btn.addEventListener('click', handleDrawerBack));
  })();
</script>


  <script>
    document.querySelector('body').classList.add('logo-left-option')
  </script>
  <script>
    class LocalizationForm extends HTMLElement {
  constructor() {
    super();
    this.elements = {
      input: this.querySelector('input[name="country_code"]'),
      button: this.querySelector('button'),
      panel: this.querySelector('ul'),
    };
    this.elements.button.addEventListener('click', this.openSelector.bind(this));
    this.elements.button.addEventListener('focusout', this.closeSelector.bind(this));
    this.addEventListener('keyup', this.onContainerKeyUp.bind(this));

    this.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(item => item.addEventListener('click', this.onItemClick.bind(this)));
  }

  hidePanel() {
    this.elements.button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
    this.elements.panel.setAttribute('hidden', true);
  }

  onContainerKeyUp(event) {
    if (event.code.toUpperCase() !== 'ESCAPE') return;

    this.hidePanel();
    this.elements.button.focus();
  }

  onItemClick(event) {
    event.preventDefault();
    const form = this.querySelector('form');
    this.elements.input.value = event.currentTarget.dataset.value;
    if (form) form.submit();
  }

  openSelector() {
     document.querySelector('#globalePopupWrapper').classList.add('globalePopupShow')
    this.elements.button.focus();
    //this.elements.panel.toggleAttribute('hidden');
    this.elements.button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', (this.elements.button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'false').toString());
  }

  closeSelector(event) {
    const shouldClose = event.relatedTarget && event.relatedTarget.nodeName === 'BUTTON';
    if (event.relatedTarget === null || shouldClose) {
      this.hidePanel();
    }
  }
}

customElements.define('localization-form', LocalizationForm);
  </script>
    

</div>

        <main class="main-content" id="MainContent">

<script>
  function customAddtoCart(event, variantId){
  fetch('/cart/add.js', {
      method: "POST",
      headers: {
        "Content-type": "application/json"
      },
      body: JSON.stringify({id: parseInt(variantId), quantity: 1})
    }).then(data => data.json())
  .then((data) => {
    window.location.href = "/cart";
  })
}
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
  document.querySelectorAll(".product-single__tab-heading").forEach((heading) => {
    heading.addEventListener("click", () => {
      // document.querySelectorAll(".product-single__tab-heading").forEach((heading2, index) => {
      //   if (heading2.classList.contains("product-single__tab-heading--active")) {
      //     heading2.classList.remove("product-single__tab-heading--active");
      //   }
      //   if (heading2.parentElement.querySelector(".product-single__tab.product-single__description[data-index='" + index + "'").classList.contains("product-single__tab--active")) {
      //     heading2.parentElement.querySelector(".product-single__tab.product-single__description[data-index='" + index + "'").classList.remove("product-single__tab--active");
      //   }
      // });
      if(!heading.classList.contains("product-single__tab-heading--active")){
        heading.classList.add("product-single__tab-heading--active");
        document.querySelector(".product-single__tabs-content .product-single__tab.product-single__description[data-index='" + heading.getAttribute("data-index") + "']").classList.add("product-single__tab--active");
      }else{
        heading.classList.remove("product-single__tab-heading--active");
        document.querySelector(".product-single__tabs-content .product-single__tab.product-single__description[data-index='" + heading.getAttribute("data-index") + "']").classList.remove("product-single__tab--active");
      }
    });
  });
   document.querySelectorAll(".main-product-how").forEach((mainProduct) => {
    mainProduct.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
      var variants = JSON.parse(mainProduct.getAttribute("data-variants"));
      var currentProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-productId");
      document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-id='"+currentProductId+"']").removeAttribute("data-related-id");
      document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-id='"+currentProductId+"']").innerHTML = "";
      if(document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-id='"+currentProductId+"']")){
        variants.forEach((mainProductVariants) => {
          var currentVariantSize = document.createElement("button");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("type", "hidden");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("product-id", currentProductId);
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("variant-id", mainProductVariants.id);
          if(mainProductVariants.available){
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute("onclick", "customAddtoCart(this,'"+mainProductVariants.id+"')");
          }else{
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option", "unavailable");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute('disabled', '');
          }
          currentVariantSize.textContent = mainProductVariants.option2;
         
          document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-id='"+currentProductId+"']").appendChild(currentVariantSize);
        });
      }
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll(".stylerecolor").forEach((mainProduct) => {
    mainProduct.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
      var variants = JSON.parse(mainProduct.getAttribute("data-variants"));
      var mainProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-main-productid");
      var currentProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-productId");
      document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").setAttribute("data-related-id", currentProductId);
      document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").innerHTML = "";
      if(document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']")){
        variants.forEach((mainProductVariants) => {
          var currentVariantSize = document.createElement("button");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("type", "hidden");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("product-id", currentProductId);
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("variant-id", mainProductVariants.id);
          if(mainProductVariants.available){
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute("onclick", "customAddtoCart(this,'"+mainProductVariants.id+"')");
          }else{
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option", "unavailable");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute('disabled', '');
          }
          currentVariantSize.textContent = mainProductVariants.option2;
         
          document.querySelector(".how-c-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").appendChild(currentVariantSize);
        });
      }
    });
  });
   const swatches = document.querySelectorAll('.variant__button-link');

  swatches.forEach(swatch => {
    swatch.addEventListener('click', function() {
      const productCard = this.closest('.custom-pdt-card');
      const swatchesInCard = productCard.querySelectorAll('.variant__button-label');
      swatchesInCard.forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
      const label = this.querySelector('.variant__button-label');
      label.classList.add('active');
      if(this.querySelector('span')){
        productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-title').innerHTML = this.querySelector('span')?.getAttribute('data-title');
      }
      if(this.querySelector('span')){
        productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-title').setAttribute('href', this.querySelector('span')?.getAttribute('data-handle'))
      }
      if(this.querySelector('span')){
        productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-img a').setAttribute('href', this.querySelector('span')?.getAttribute('data-handle'))
      }
      const mainImage = productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-img img');
      const newImage = this.getAttribute('data-image');
      if (mainImage && newImage) {
        mainImage.src = mainImage.src = newImage;
      }
      
    });
  });
});
</script>

    var splide = new Splide('#splide', {

      perMove: 1,
      pagination : false,
    });

    splide.mount();

<script>
function moreColors(event){
  event.parentElement.classList.add("show-colors");
  event.parentElement.classList.add("loading");
  setTimeout(() => {
    event.parentElement.classList.remove("loading");
  }, 1000);
}
function customAddtoCart(event, variantId){
 document.querySelectorAll('.c-card-product_option button[type="button"]').forEach((activeList) => {
   if(activeList.classList.contains('size-active')){
     activeList.classList.remove('size-active');
   }
 })
 event.classList.add('size-active');
 const variantInputField = document.querySelector('.shopify-product-form .variant-id');
  variantInputField.setAttribute('value', variantId);  
  const addToCartSubmitButton = document.querySelector('.shopify-product-form .addtocart-submit');
  if (addToCartSubmitButton) {
      addToCartSubmitButton.click();
  } 
}
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
if(!document.querySelector("#completeset #completeset-list div")){
  document.querySelector("#tab_new_rd_1").classList.remove("active");
  document.querySelector("li[data-id='tab_new_rd_1']").classList.remove("active");
  document.querySelector("li[data-id='tab_new_rd_2']").classList.add("active");
  document.querySelector("#tab_new_rd_2").classList.add("active");
}
document.querySelectorAll('.custom-pdt-card .plus-filter-btn').forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        // Add 'is-open' class to the closest '.pdt-card-img'
        button.closest('.custom-pdt-card').querySelector('.pdt-card-img').classList.add('is-open');
        
        // Add 'quick-view-open' class to the body
        document.body.classList.add('quick-view-open');
    });
});
  setTimeout(() => {
    if (document.querySelectorAll('.rd_colletion_tab li').length > 0) {
        document.querySelectorAll('.rd_colletion_tab li').forEach(function(this_loop) {
            this_loop.addEventListener('click', function() {
                var id = this.getAttribute('data-id');
                document.querySelectorAll('.rd_colletion_tab li').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                this.classList.add('active');
                const targetTabContent = document.getElementById(id);
                const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.custom_colletion_tab__col');
                tabContents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
                targetTabContent.classList.add('active');
            });
        });
    }
  }, 1000);
  document.querySelectorAll(".main-product").forEach((mainProduct) => {
    mainProduct.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
      if(mainProduct.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.previousElementSibling.querySelector('a')){
        mainProduct.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.previousElementSibling.querySelector('a').setAttribute('onclick', 'recentlyViewed("'+mainProduct.dataset.productid+'")');
      }
      var variants = JSON.parse(mainProduct.getAttribute("data-variants"));
      var currentProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-productId");
      document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+currentProductId+"']").removeAttribute("data-related-id");
      document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+currentProductId+"']").innerHTML = "";
      if(document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+currentProductId+"']")){
        variants.forEach((mainProductVariants) => {
          var currentVariantSize = document.createElement("button");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("type", "hidden");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("product-id", currentProductId);
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("variant-id", mainProductVariants.id);
          if(mainProductVariants.available){
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute("onclick", "customAddtoCart(this,'"+mainProductVariants.id+"')");
          }else{
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option", "unavailable");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute('disabled', '');
          }
          currentVariantSize.textContent = mainProductVariants.option2;
          var currentActiveTab = "";
          if(document.querySelector("#tab_new_rd_1").classList.contains("active")){
            currentActiveTab = "#tab_new_rd_1";
          }else{
            currentActiveTab = "#tab_new_rd_2";
          }
          document.querySelector(""+currentActiveTab+" .c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+currentProductId+"']").appendChild(currentVariantSize);
        });
      }
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll(".related-colors").forEach((mainProduct) => {
    mainProduct.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
      if(mainProduct.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.previousElementSibling.querySelector('a')){
        mainProduct.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.previousElementSibling.querySelector('a').setAttribute('onclick', 'recentlyViewed("'+mainProduct.dataset.productid+'")');
      }
      var variants = JSON.parse(mainProduct.getAttribute("data-variants"));
      var mainProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-main-productid");
      var currentProductId = mainProduct.getAttribute("data-productId");
      document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").setAttribute("data-related-id", currentProductId);
      document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").innerHTML = "";
      if(document.querySelector(".c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']")){
        variants.forEach((mainProductVariants) => {
          var currentVariantSize = document.createElement("button");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("type", "hidden");
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("product-id", currentProductId);
          currentVariantSize.setAttribute("variant-id", mainProductVariants.id);
          if(mainProductVariants.available){
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute("onclick", "customAddtoCart(this,'"+mainProductVariants.id+"')");
          }else{
            currentVariantSize.classList.add("size-option", "unavailable");
            currentVariantSize.setAttribute('disabled', '');
          }
          currentVariantSize.textContent = mainProductVariants.option2;
          var currentActiveTab = "";
          if(document.querySelector("#tab_new_rd_1").classList.contains("active")){
            currentActiveTab = "#tab_new_rd_1";
          }else{
            currentActiveTab = "#tab_new_rd_2";
          }
          document.querySelector(""+currentActiveTab+" .c-card-product_option[data-Id='"+mainProductId+"']").appendChild(currentVariantSize);
        });
      }
    });
  });
  
  const swatches = document.querySelectorAll('.variant__button-link');

  swatches.forEach(swatch => {
    swatch.addEventListener('click', function() {
      if(this.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('.pdt-card-img a')){
        this.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('.pdt-card-img a').setAttribute('onclick', 'recentlyViewed(this, "'+this.parentElement.dataset.productid+'")');
      }
      // Find the closest product card to the clicked swatch
      const productCard = this.closest('.custom-pdt-card');

      // Remove 'active' class from all swatches within the same product card
      const swatchesInCard = productCard.querySelectorAll('.variant__button-label');
      swatchesInCard.forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));

      // Add 'active' class to the clicked swatch
      const label = this.querySelector('.variant__button-label');
      label.classList.add('active');

      // Update the main image for the clicked product card
      const mainImage = productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-img img.featured-image');
      const newImage = this.getAttribute('data-image');
      if (mainImage && newImage) {
        mainImage.src = mainImage.src = newImage;
      }
      const mainImage2 = productCard.querySelector('.pdt-card-img img.hover-image');
      if(mainImage2){
        if(this.hasAttribute('data-image2')){
          const newImage2 = this.getAttribute('data-image2');
          if (mainImage2 && newImage2) {
            mainImage2.src = mainImage2.src = newImage2;
            mainImage2.classList.remove('visually-hidden');
          }
        }else{
          mainImage2.classList.add('visually-hidden');
        }
      }
    });
  });

new Splide('#completeset', {
  perPage: 4,         // Number of slides to display at once
  perMove: 1,         // Number of slides to move when the arrow is clicked
  autoplay: false,    // Disables auto sliding
  pagination: false,  // Disables pagination
  arrows: true,       // Displays navigation arrows
  breakpoints: {
    768: {
      perPage: 1,    // Display one slide per page on screens less than 768px wide
      width: '100%', // Full width for the first product
      padding: {
        right: '24%', // Show 1/3 of the next product (100% - 33.333% = 66.666%)
      },
    }
  }
}).mount();
});


 

</script>

</div>

<script>    
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const targetNode = document.body;
      const config = { childList: true, subtree: true };
      const callback = function(mutationsList, observer) {
        for (let mutation of mutationsList) {
          if (mutation.type === 'childList') {
            let recommendationBlock1 = document.querySelector('.recently-viewed-pdp .recs-recentview-slider');
            if (recommendationBlock1) {
               targetNode.classList.add('loaded1');
                var splide = new Splide( '.recently-viewed-pdp .recs-recentview-slider', {
    			perPage: 4,
    			perMove: 1,
    			autoplay: false,
    			pagination: false,
    			arrows: true,
    			breakpoints: {
    				768: {
    					perPage: 1,
    					width: '100%',
    					padding: {
    						right: '24%',
    					},
    				},
  			},
		});
          
		splide.mount();
              
              observer.disconnect();
              break;
            }
          }
        }
      };
      const observer = new MutationObserver(callback);
      observer.observe(targetNode, config);
      });
  </script>


</div>

  };
  function mergeObject(obj1, obj2){
    var obj3 = {};
    for (var attr in obj1) { obj3[attr] = obj1[attr]; }
    for (var attr in obj2) { obj3[attr] = obj2[attr]; }
    return obj3;
  }
  if (typeof boostPFSConfig == 'undefined') {
    boostPFSConfig = {};
  }
  if (typeof boostPFSAppConfig != 'undefined') {
    boostPFSConfig = mergeObject(boostPFSConfig, boostPFSAppConfig);
  }
  if (typeof boostPFSThemeConfig != 'undefined') {
    boostPFSConfig = mergeObject(boostPFSConfig, boostPFSThemeConfig);
  }
</script>

       /**On Scroll Fixed**/

      <script>
      window.addEventListener('load', function() {
      var _learnq = window._learnq || [];
      function addedToCart() {
        fetch(`${window.location.origin}/cart.js`)
        .then(res => res.clone().json().then(data => {
          var cart = {
            total_price: data.total_price/100,
            $value: data.total_price/100,
            total_discount: data.total_discount,
            original_total_price: data.original_total_price/100,
            items: data.items
          }
          if (item !== 'undefined') {
            cart = Object.assign(cart, item)
          }
          if (klAjax) {
              _learnq.push(['track', 'Added to Cart', cart]);
              klAjax = false;
            }
        }))
      };
      (function (ns, fetch) {
        ns.fetch = function() {
          const response = fetch.apply(this, arguments);
          response.then(res => {
            if (`${window.location.origin}/cart/add.js`
              .includes(res.url)) {
                  addedToCart()
            }
          });
          return response
        }
      }(window, window.fetch));
      var klAjax = true;
      var atcButtons = document.querySelectorAll("form[action*='/cart/add'] button[type='submit']");
      for (var i = 0; i < atcButtons.length; i++) {
          atcButtons[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
            if (klAjax) {
              _learnq.push(['track', 'Added to Cart', item]);
              klAjax = false;
            }
          })
      }
      });
      </script>

<script>
  
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  document.querySelector('.modelDisclosure .disclosure__button').addEventListener('click', (countryBtn) => {
  document.querySelector('#ModelCountryList').classList.toggle('ModelCountryList-show');
  countryBtn.target.classList.toggle('btn-open')
});

  document.querySelector('.modelDisclosure .disclosure__button').setAttribute('data-value', ariaCurrentTrue)
document.querySelectorAll('#ModelCountryList li').forEach((cListItem) => {
  cListItem.querySelector('a').addEventListener('click', (cSItem) => {
    cSItem.preventDefault();
    document.querySelector('.modelDisclosure .disclosure__button').setAttribute('data-value', cSItem.target.getAttribute('data-value'))
    document.querySelector('.modelDisclosure .disclosure__button span').innerHTML = cSItem.target.textContent;
    document.querySelector('.modelDisclosure .disclosure__button').classList.toggle('btn-open');
    document.querySelector('#ModelCountryList').classList.toggle('ModelCountryList-show');
  });
});

document.querySelector('.gl-DefaultBtn.gl-SaveBtn').addEventListener('click', () => {
  const popupDataVal = document.querySelector('.globale_popup_wrapper button.disclosure__button').getAttribute('data-value');
  setTimeout(() => {
      document.querySelector(`.hdr-disclosure-list li a[data-value="${popupDataVal}"]`).click();
  }, 500);
});

    document.querySelector('.globale_popup_wrapper').classList.remove('globalePopupShow');
});
  document.querySelector('.globale_overlay').addEventListener('click', function() {
    document.querySelector('.globale_popup_wrapper').classList.remove('globalePopupShow');
});

})

    <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        let lastClear = localStorage.getItem("lastClear");
        
        if (!lastClear || Date.now() - lastClear > 86400000) {
          document.cookie.split(";").forEach(c => {
            let parts = c.split("=");
            if (parts.length < 2) return;
            let cookieName = parts[0].trim();
            let paths = ["/", "/cart", "/checkout", "/account"];
            let domains = ["", location.hostname, "." + location.hostname];
            paths.forEach(path => {
              domains.forEach(domain => {
                document.cookie = `${cookieName}=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=${path}` + (domain ? `; domain=${domain}` : "");
              });
            });
            console.log("After Clearing:", cookieName);
          });
      
          localStorage.setItem("lastClear", Date.now());
          console.log("Cookies Cleared. First-time visit or 24-hour interval passed.");
        } else {
          console.log("Cookies not cleared. Interval not reached.");
        }
        console.log("Cookies After Clearing:", document.cookie);
      });
    </script>

  <script>
    const RECENTLY_VIEWED_KEY = 'selectedProductIds';
    const TEMP_PRODUCT_KEY = 'tempProductId';
    const MAX_ITEMS = 10;
    recentlyViewedPageLoad(9043407667431);
    function updateRecentlyViewed(newId){
      let storedIds = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(RECENTLY_VIEWED_KEY)) || [];
      storedIds = storedIds.filter((id) => id !== newId);
      storedIds.unshift(newId);
      if (storedIds.length > MAX_ITEMS) {
          storedIds = storedIds.slice(0, MAX_ITEMS);
      }
      localStorage.setItem(RECENTLY_VIEWED_KEY, JSON.stringify(storedIds));
    };
    function recentlyViewed(productId){
      const tempProductId = localStorage.getItem(TEMP_PRODUCT_KEY);
      if (tempProductId) {
          updateRecentlyViewed(tempProductId);
      }
      localStorage.setItem(TEMP_PRODUCT_KEY, productId);
    }
    function recentlyViewedPageLoad(productId){
      const tempProductId = localStorage.getItem(TEMP_PRODUCT_KEY);
      localStorage.setItem(TEMP_PRODUCT_KEY, productId);
    }
  </script>
  <script>
        // Observer 1
        var targetElement1 = document.querySelector(".product-price");
        if (targetElement1) {
            var observer1 = new MutationObserver(function(mutations) {
                mutations.forEach(function(mutation) {
                    if (mutation.type === 'childList' && mutation.target.querySelector(".square-placement")) {
                        var squarePlacement = mutation.target.querySelector(".square-placement");
                        document.querySelector(".grid__item.medium-up--one-third form").appendChild(squarePlacement);
                    }
                });
            });

            var config1 = { attributes: true,subtree: true, childList: true };
            observer1.observe(targetElement1, config1);
        }

        /* afterpay */
       // Function to observe changes in the shadow DOM
    function observeShadowDOM(shadowRoot) {
        const config = { childList: true, subtree: true };
        const callback = function(mutationsList, observer) {
            for (const mutation of mutationsList) {
                if (mutation.type === 'childList') {
                    const pElement = shadowRoot.querySelector("p");
                    if (pElement) {
                      if(!shadowRoot.querySelector("style[data-provider='custom']")){
                        var colorChangeStyle = document.createElement("style");
                        colorChangeStyle.setAttribute("data-provider", "custom");
                        colorChangeStyle.innerHTML = 'p{font-size:11px !important; letter-spacing: normal !important;} .afterpay-logo.brand-afterpay, .afterpay-logo.brand-afterpay svg {height: 44px;width: 64px !important;}';
                        shadowRoot.appendChild(colorChangeStyle);
                      }else{
                        shadowRoot.querySelector("style[data-provider='custom']").innerHTML = "p{font-size:11px !important; letter-spacing: normal !important;} .afterpay-logo.brand-afterpay, .afterpay-logo.brand-afterpay svg {height: 44px;width: 64px !important;}";
                      }
                        
                      observer.disconnect(); // Stop observing after the desired change is made
                      break;
                    }
                }
            }
        };

        const observer = new MutationObserver(callback);
        observer.observe(shadowRoot, config);
    }

    // Function to move squarePlacement next to addToCartButton
    function moveSquarePlacement() {
        const squarePlacement = document.querySelector('square-placement');
        const addToCartButton = document.querySelector('.btn.add-to-cart.product-form__submit');

        if (squarePlacement && addToCartButton) {
            addToCartButton.insertAdjacentElement('afterend', squarePlacement);
        }
    }

    // Function to observe changes in the main DOM
    function observeDOM() {
        const targetNode = document.querySelector("#MainContent .grid__item.medium-up--one-third .product-price");
        const config = { childList: true, subtree: true };
        const callback = function(mutationsList, observer) {
            for (const mutation of mutationsList) {
                if (mutation.type === 'childList') {
                    const squarePlacement = document.querySelector('square-placement');
                    if (squarePlacement) {
                        const mediaQuery = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 767px)');
                       // if (mediaQuery.matches) {
                            if (squarePlacement.shadowRoot) {
                                observeShadowDOM(squarePlacement.shadowRoot); // Start observing the shadow DOM
                            }
                      //  }

                        moveSquarePlacement();
                        observer.disconnect(); // Stop observing the main DOM after finding squarePlacement
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }
        };

        const observer = new MutationObserver(callback);
        observer.observe(targetNode, config);
    }

    observeDOM();
    document.querySelector(".size-guide-button button").addEventListener("click", () => {
      document.body.classList.add('js-drawer-open');
      document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.add('is-transitioning');
      document.querySelector(".size-guide-button button").setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
      document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.add('drawer--is-open');
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.remove('is-transitioning');
      },900)
    });
    document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer button.js-drawer-close").addEventListener("click", () => {
      document.body.classList.remove('js-drawer-open');
      document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.add('is-transitioning');
      document.querySelector(".size-guide-button button").setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.remove('drawer--is-open');
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.querySelector("#SizeGuideDrawer").classList.remove('is-transitioning');
      },900)
    });
